<%= form_for mural do |f| %>
<%= f.hidden_field :artist_id, value:  set_artist_by_id.id %>
Please give us a little information about where the mural is located:  <%= f.text_field :location_details%><br>
Location: <%= f.collection_select :neighborhood_id, Neighborhood.all, :id, :name, include_blank: 'Please select a location' %><br>
Don't see the neighborhood please add it
<%= f.fields_for :neighborhood, mural.build_neighborhood do |neighborhood_fields|%>
  <%= neighborhood_fields.text_field :name%><br>
<% end %>
Check if mural is currently active?  <%= f.check_box :active %><br>
<%= f.label :add_picture %>
<%= f.file_field :avatar %>
<%= f.submit %>
<% end %>
